thailand reduc main rice crop project thailand 's main paddi crop is expect to fall to 15.4 mln tonn in the 1986/87 ( nov/oct ) season from a previou 15.68 mln estim in novemb and an actual 17.35 mln a year ago , the thai rice mill associ said . it said a joint field survey late last month by the associ , the commerc ministri and the bank of thailand indic that paddi output in thailand 's northeast region is lower than expect becaus of a drought in sever provinc . the associ said rice grow area in nakhon ratchasima , chaiyaphum , khon kaen and mahasarakam were especi affect by low rainfal in the second half of 1986. it said last novemb that the drought reduc total nation area sown with paddi to some 8.25 mln hectar thi year , down from 8.84 mln a year ago . the main crop repres about 85 pct of thailand 's paddi output .